text: One of the most extrovert guy I ever met. You were a wonderful friend in your own way. All the trips we been on, all the calls everyday to go somewhere, all the nights we been high xD and unlimited memories together, I will always cherish them all. Thank you for being one of the reasons I love IITK.
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text:
Bhai.. Tera kitna bhi mazak udaya ho.. Ek baat yaad rakhna.. Duniya ka sabse cool insan tu hi hai.. Dil ka itna saaf banda kabhi nahi dekha..
Memory kamzor hai kya bc? Fifa me mai harata tha tujhe lol.. Madrid ki match dekhna, Rishab ke maze lena, first year ki kitni bakchodi.. College life itni bakchod tum sab ke wajah se hi hui hai bhai.. Mini militia toh kabhi nahi bhulunga..
Bas ek regret rahega bhai.. Aakhri baar tumse milne nahi aa paya mai bas.. Ummeed karta hu kabhi milenge.. Bohot bakchodi baaki hai paki..
Tera private dance baaki hai ek nachaniya.. Milne aana kabhi campus!
PS- MTH me chaapa tha dono ne.. Kya hase the bhai uss din
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text:
You are one of the most genuine guys I ever met.. Aaj bhi saari trips yaad hai.. Mussoorie, Delhi, Goa.. Saari Antaragni ki raate, aur kya kya nahi.. 
Mussoorie me walk karte karte kaha pohoch gaye the bhai lol.. Maze aa gaye the.. 
Zindagi me fodte aaye ho, aage bhi fodte rehna.. 
Aur aisi hi personality rehne dena..
All the best bhai.. Aur milte rahenge surely!
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text: Cheers to the drunk Antaragni nights. I won't ever forget those. It was a pleasure knowing you. All the best!

text:

Techkriti ke interview ki tayyari, saari parties, Antaragni, saari bakchodi.. Everything will be missed.
Ek trip plan karo ab aur chalo sab bas..

text: Bro, you are one of the most creative person I ever met. By far! Thanks for all the great "stuff". How can I forget the moments Dbot tried to teach you Hindi. All the best bro!
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text:
Abe mote, aakhri baar sandwich toh khila de.. Bhai yaar ab kya kya likhu yaha? Cricket me ek over me 5 sixes, uske baad comeback, Pankaj ki kahani pe zor se hasna, GoT, ek dusri ki maarna.. Jagah kam pad jaegi yaha.. Bhai 4 saal kaise nikal gaye pata hi nahi chala.. Still I remember the first time we met... Mess me tu bagal me aake baith gaya aur fried rice khilaya tha tune.. Tab socha tha yaar ye kaun banda hai? Pet ke saath saath tera dil bhi bohot bada hai bhai.. Dbot ke bahar baran pe kaise hase the kabhi nahi bhulunga.. Tera mujhe kutta kehna kabhi nahi bhulunga bhai. Aur kattar hindu banna nahi bhulunga.. 
Bas do gham hai. Ek toh aakhri baar campus nahi aa paya bhaiyo se milne aur dusra tere sath trip nahi hui kabhi. Ek toh puri ho sakti hai bhai. Chalte hai jab ye log udhar wapas dede.. Love you shanna thane bhai...
Jai Shree Ram!
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text: Aur bhai Doga.. Teri kahaniya bohot bakchod hua karti thi though kabhi extreme ho jati thi xD. Aise hi bakchod rehna bhai..

text:
Bhai zerodha pe account ban gaya? Lol.. First interaction toh yaad nahi.. Par class ke bahar assignment chaapna yaad hai.. Antaragni ki bakchodi yaad hai.. Delhi ki trip yaad hai.. Hamleys me ghuske chutiyapa karna yaad hai..
Kash yaar aakhri baar campus milne aa sakta tum sabse..
Tere captions bohot danger the bhai... Maze aa gaye the padhke..
Kabhi ye bakchodi kam mat hone dena bro.. Tu unme se hai jinhe mai ekdum chaapu maanta hu. Aise hi chaapte raho bc. Aur milo kabhi!

Milte hai jaani

text: Bhai, tum bohot hi genuine bande ho.. Aur Samarth ko kaise jhel liya tumne ye bata dena bas lol.. Suna hai tum bhi dual kar rahe ho aur peena shuru kar diye ho.. Agle saal sath me bakchodi karenge bhai.. Aao campus jald

text:
I still remember the first time we met when I beat you in pool xD. You have been one of the most important person in my life and I hope you always will be. All the bakchodi, trips, watching streams, deep talks and what not, it will always be close to my heart. Remember, no matter what, I am always just a call away brother. Gurgaon aaunga (aauga xD) jald and phir se bakchodiya shuru.
PS- Don't give up on our startup idea lol.
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text:
Tu aur Rohan.. Main reason meri campus life itni bakchod rahi hai.. Love you brother! 
PS- I realised bohot kam likha tere liye.. Par agar sab likhne baith gaya toh yearbook me sirf tera hi section rahega xD...
Jaldi mil aur ummeed hai Gurgaon sath hi rahege
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani

text:
Abe mujhe nahi laga tha tere liye bhi memoir likhna hai.. Ek tu hi hai jiske liye likhna sabse mushkil hoga.. Jo bhi likhu kam hai aur kuch na kuch reh jaega.. Sabse pehle toh dil se shukriya bc randirona sunne ke liye.. Bc tu nahi hota toh kya hota.. Main main keywords toh tune daal diye. Agar sab keywords daalne baithe toh bhi bhar jaega ye yearbook. Phir bhi dekhte hai..
Gadhi pe hasna, tera oyozone hona, TA ki gand maarna, meri tatti kismat pe rona, paper se pehle sath me hagna, tere bhand hone ke baad baate sunna, Hall 7 toh nahi bhulunga bhai, First year me Pandey ko pareshan karna, OAT ‚ù§Ô∏è, mujhe ulti karake sulane ke liye thanks, mera rr roz sunna, kattar hindu banna (Jai Shree Ram), Pankaj ke maze lena, din bhar tere room me pade rehna, bhai summer kaise bhul gaya tu, kaise pada rehta tha mai tere room me ü§£, roz 12 baje tujhe canteen bulana, Rishab tu aur mai bakchodi karna, tere aur Rishab ke jhagde aur usme mai aag lagata tha ü§£, gandu ek aur bhul gaya tu - Phy103 ke paper ke ek raat pehle library me bakchodi karna, 8-10 bhaiyo pe hasna, MOS dono baar (A ya B toh lag hi jaega madarchod ü§£), class bunk karke ccd canteen jana, Das ki dukaan, tujhe pehli baar daaru pilana, tera bihari naam karan karna, aauga bolna, subah YJHD dekhna aur gaane me background dancer pe hasna...
Aur kitna kuch hai bsdk..
Aakhri ek saal toh isse jyada bakchodi karni hai, ab paisa bhi hoga üòå, pure 4 saal ki khunnas ek me nikal lenge.. Khulega campus bhai.. Bakchodiya baaki hai... College life meri itni bakchod huyi hai aur safal huyi hai toh uska main reason Tu aur Rishab ho.. Love you brother.

PS- Mujhe ab bhi yaad hai pehli baar kaise mile the.. Paki ke room pe tu nanga khada tha aur tab sirf apan dono the jinko Dani pasand thi.. Dani is lub ‚ù§Ô∏è
Tab ye expect nahi kiya tha apan aise dost banege..
(Unexpected friendships are the best ones)
Jaldi mil bsdk. Saal ke upar ho gaya!
author: Pranav Hitesh Dasani
